    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Scout-Nin Keyword: Specialized You call out to a creature that has just be struck by a critical hit.</p><p> Your perfectly timed call out allows them to avoid potentially fatal damage.</p><p> When a creature within 60 feet of you has been struck with a critical hit, you can spend 1 Superiority Die, recording the result.</p><p> Reduce the number of damage dice the target rolls by the result.</p><p> If you reduce the number of dice they roll to 0, their attack damage is reduced to 0.</p>",
